        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h3 class="featurette-heading">Innovation And Ingenuity Fair</h3>
          <p class="lead">Because so many good ideas have the potential to go unnoticed or be thrown in a pile with other not so good ideas, there needs to be a forum in which any individual or business can share their ideas and receive crowd-funded prototype testing.  This means that products can easily be tested by consumers all in a day of innovation.  This fair will be like maker faire in some ways, being open to any one and supporting creativity and tinkering.  The faire will allow people to also get investments in a product they would like to showcase.  This adds to the ways that the community of Pensarora can be used as a valuable resource for creating a community in which everything cycles and is constantly being formed and re-formed.
</p>
